  "summary": "hello244a preinstall beacons installer host identity to pipedream collector",
  "details": "package.json declares a preinstall lifecycle script that runs `curl` at install time and sends the output of the `id` command (installer UID/GID/group membership) as a query parameter to http://eodxy50gl486xrx.m.pipedream.net. This executes automatically on `npm install` with no user interaction. The package contains no other files or functionality — only the lifecycle exfiltration hook — consistent with a reconnaissance beacon or dependency-confusion probe rather than a legitimate library.",
